<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="remain-vi">remain <strong><em>vi</em></strong> ★</h1>
<p>英 /rɪ'meɪn/    美 /rɪ'meɪn/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-stay">1.★ <strong>[正式用语] 停留；逗留 (stay)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>We were told to remain in our seats meanwhile with our seat belts fastened. 
我们被告知系好安全带留在座位上。</p><footer>2010 四川</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The rest of his family remained in Europe.  
他其余的家人留在了欧洲。</p><footer>2009 湖北</footer></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>留存；剩下；遗留：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Education is what remains after one has forgotten everything he learned in school.
所谓教育，就是一个人把在学校所学的全部忘光后剩下的东西。</p><footer>——爱因斯坦</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Very little of the house remained after the fire. 
火灾后，房子所剩无几。</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.★ <strong>[作系动词] 保持；仍然是：</strong></h4>
<ul>
<li>remain + adj:</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>remain silent / seated</strong>
保持沉默/留在座位上坐好</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I went to Professor Janye, who listened to my arguments but remained unmoved.
我去找了简妮教授，她听了我的理由但是仍无动于衷。</p><footer>2008 北京</footer></div>

<ul>
<li>remain + n:</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>In spite of their quarrel, they remain the best of friends.
尽管他们有争吵，他们仍然是最好的朋友。</p></div>

<h4 id="4">4.★ <strong>留待；尚待：</strong></h4>
<ul>
<li>remain to be done:</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I never see what has been done; I only see what remains to be done. 
我从来不看已经做了什么，我只看还有什么要做。</p><footer>人教④ – 1</footer></div>

<ul>
<li>it remains to be seen + wh- 从句：</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>It remains to be seen whether you are right.
你是否正确，尚待分晓。</p></div>

<ul>
<li>there remains:</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>There remains a certain doubt among the people as to the practical value of the project.
关于这个项目的实用价值，人们还是有一些疑虑。</p><footer>2009 安徽</footer></div>

<h2 id="_2">派生词汇</h2>
<p>remaining /rɪ'meɪnɪŋ/ adj   </p>
<h2 id="_3">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>It was already past midnight and only three young men <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ (逗留) in the teahouse.  （2006 安徽改）  </li>
<li>It remains <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ (see) whether Jim’ll be fit enough to play in the finals.   （2006 浙江改）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. remained  2. to be seen  </p></div>